  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Public Information Campaign on Awareness Raising of Human Trafficking and Exploitation in Post COVID-19 Environment</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of this campaign will bring the issue of human trafficking into public consciousness, to raise awareness of who might be a person in a trafficking situation and to highlight that victims can, often, be hiding in plain sight. The campaign will use a variety of media to include social media as well as print and on street visibility placed in strategic locations such as city centre and town centre locations, Dublin airport, Bus Aras, and travel hubs.</narrative>
  </description>
